description:
Get 5 exclusive liveries for the most popular cars in V-Rally 4:
• Porsche 911 RGT 997 (Rally)
• Volkswagen Polo RX (V-Rally Cross)
• Tatum Class 10 (Buggy)
• Volkswagen Polo R WRC (Rally)
• Ford Mustang Fastback (Extreme-Khana)
These new liveries are available in all game modes.
name: V-Rally 4 - Supercharge Pack
